    public class BackwardFastMultiNodeDijkstra
extends FastMultiNodeDijkstra
implements BackwardMultiNodePathCalculator
    This implementation of a backwards routing Dijkstra is based on an inverted network, i.e. a network were the links' from and to nodes are switched.
